    1. sell 100 items (back-order: 100)
    2. purchase 75 items (back-order: 25 / invoice -1201)
    3. sell 100 items (back-order: 25 @ -1201 / 100 @ -1203)
    4. purchase 75 (back-order: 0 @ -1201 / 50 @ -1203)
